<div class=3D"bbWrapper">This is going to be one of those simple "puts two =
words together for a name" things. So far I have:<br>
<br>
Blood<br>
Ice<br>
Death<br>
Kill<br>
Raven<br>
Hawk<br>
Bane<br>
Spawn<br>
Stone<br>
Snap<br>
Hunter<br>
Arm<br>
Shot<br>
Ghost<br>
<br>
Suggest additions to the list! Or point me toward an existing generator if =
you know one!<br>
<br>
Background: I'm running a supers game, starting by filling in various histo=
rical eras and then doing the modern setting. Currently we are doing Team U=
SA vs. Team USSR in 1991 Lithuania, done in the approximate style of the fi=
rst round of Image comics. I need a bunch of throwaway references to other =
contemporary heroes.</div>

=09

	=09
		=09
	=09

	=09
=09

			=09
			</div>

