 crazy. Actually, hell, that's his 90s origin. He's a cybernetically enhanc=
ed soldier from a dark future, sent back in time to try and prevent that da=
rk future from occuring.<br>
<br>
Brain Scream - A psychic whose psionic fury can barely be contained<br>
<br>
Ghost-sama - The ghost of the last member of a murdered ninja clan<br>
<br>
Necrocore - When Colonel Crazy came back in time, he brought with him the c=
entral computer core of the resistance base, and installed it within a Adav=
ibranium Ex-Terminator Endoskelton that looks suspiciously like the Termina=
tor.<br>
<br>
Captain Falcon Mantis - I feel like all questions about Captain Falcon Mant=
is are answered by the name Captain Falcon Mantis.<br>
<br>
Grimtron - I just assume this is dollar store Grimlock.<br>
<br>
Midnight Hunter - This has gotta be a real 90s hero.</div>

